555
00:41:08,581 --> 00:41:10,841
but I only had one piece of paper.

556
00:41:11,716 --> 00:41:13,561
Now, it's my turn.

557
00:41:13,561 --> 00:41:16,056
"From Nuengdiao to Palm."

558
00:41:20,383 --> 00:41:22,810
"You changed my world.

559
00:41:22,810 --> 00:41:24,503
I like watching you.

560
00:41:24,503 --> 00:41:26,415
I like looking into your eyes.

561
00:41:26,415 --> 00:41:29,151
I like the mole under your eye.

562
00:41:29,956 --> 00:41:32,154
I think it's your charming point.

563
00:41:32,154 --> 00:41:35,312
I like it when you fight to protect those who are weaker.

564
00:41:36,062 --> 00:41:39,720
I like when you play lame jokes.

565
00:41:40,573 --> 00:41:42,589
It's your unique characteristic.

566
00:41:42,589 --> 00:41:45,530
You pay attention and remember small details.

567
00:41:45,530 --> 00:41:48,230
I like when you wear a Hawaiian shirt.

568
00:41:49,056 --> 00:41:52,503
I like your hairstyle when you worked as my bodyguard.

569
00:41:52,503 --> 00:41:54,936
I admire the love that you have for your mom.

570
00:41:54,936 --> 00:41:59,324
I like that you are a boyfriend who lets me hug and touch you the way I want,

571
00:41:59,324 --> 00:42:01,762
without showing any sign of annoyance."

572
00:42:04,551 --> 00:42:07,057
Why didn't you tell me that you liked my hairstyle when I was your bodyguard?

573
00:42:07,057 --> 00:42:08,816
I'll do that hairstyle forever.

574
00:42:08,816 --> 00:42:11,499
