575
00:42:11,499 --> 00:42:14,719
For you, I'll do it anytime.

576
00:42:27,995 --> 00:42:30,137
It's so windy as if it will start to rain soon.

577
00:42:30,137 --> 00:42:33,340
But it's still sunny.

578
00:42:34,344 --> 00:42:38,460
Maybe we successfully reversed the curse.

579
00:42:40,543 --> 00:42:45,043
I don't know. We did everything the fortune teller told us to do.

580
00:42:45,785 --> 00:42:48,005
There's nothing else we can do.

581
00:42:50,937 --> 00:42:53,357
Maybe this is the end for us.

582
00:42:53,357 --> 00:42:54,830
I don't know.

583
00:42:54,830 --> 00:42:57,520
I think we should focus on today and right now,

584
00:42:57,520 --> 00:43:00,240
and try to take care of each other as best as we can.

585
00:43:00,854 --> 00:43:04,334
I hope that we can grow old together like the Lord and his servant.

586
00:43:45,162 --> 00:43:47,716
[Two weeks later]

587
00:43:50,107 --> 00:43:54,187
